    <item>
      <title>惠特默表示她 100% 支持拜登，否认紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/whitmer-says-she-s-100-behind-biden-dismissing-talk-of-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根州州长格雷琴·惠特默表示，她很自豪支持总统乔·拜登成为民主党候选人，并反驳了有关拜登在上周辩论中遇到困难后她的团队与拜登竞选团队之间存在紧张关系的说法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/whitmer-says-she-s-100-behind-biden-dismissing-talk-of-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京将举行知事选举，岸田文雄命运关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/tokyo-set-to-elect-governor-in-race-key-to-kishida-s-fortunes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末，东京将决定是否重新选举一位得到首相岸田文雄领导的自民党支持的知事，还是选择一位反对派支持的挑战者，这对陷入困境的首相来说将是一次新的考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/tokyo-set-to-elect-governor-in-race-key-to-kishida-s-fortunes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国大选进入第二轮，各主要政党互相竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/main-french-parties-court-rivals-as-vote-heads-to-second-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着法国立法机构选举第二轮之争演变为议会席位的疯狂争夺，法国各大政治团体的领导人开始接触各个政治派别的选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/main-french-parties-court-rivals-as-vote-heads-to-second-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普豁免裁决或将选举审判推迟至 2025 年或更晚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-immunity-ruling-may-push-election-trial-to-2025-or-beyond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院周一裁定，总统对其“官方”行为享有一定豁免权，有关唐纳德·特朗普试图推翻 2020 年大选结果的刑事审判可能会被推迟一年或更长时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-immunity-ruling-may-push-election-trial-to-2025-or-beyond</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国大会通过中国支持的人工智能决议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/un-general-assembly-adopts-china-backed-resolution-on-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国大会通过了一项由中国牵头的决议，旨在帮助贫穷国家从人工智能中受益，这是北京和华盛顿在全球舞台上争夺人工智能霸权的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/un-general-assembly-adopts-china-backed-resolution-on-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
